---
---
<section class="hero" id="home">

  <div class="hero-kv-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
    <img src="/kv-pattern2.jpg" alt="" class="hero-kv" />
    <div class="hero-kv-overlay"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Web Director</p>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          地域とつなぐ、<br />世界とつなぐ。
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">地域事業者さまのデジタル参謀（CMO）</p>
        <p class="hero-desc">
          上場企業にて経営戦略業務に従事しながら、個人事業主として
          地域の中小企業さまの商材を全国・世界に発信していく
          デジタル支援を複業で行っています。
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">まずは相談する →</a>
          <a href="#works" class="btn-outline">実績を見る</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">6<small>+</small></span>
        <span class="stat-text">支援実績</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-sep"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">3</span>
        <span class="stat-text">コアサービス</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-sep"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">10<small>+</small></span>
        <span class="stat-text">対応ツール</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-sep"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">4<small>年</small></span>
        <span class="stat-text">支援経験</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding-top: 68px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--bg);
}

/* ── KV background ── */
.hero-kv-wrap {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 0;
}

.hero-kv {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center;
}

.hero-kv-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(
    to right,
    rgba(255,255,255,1) 0%,
    rgba(255,255,255,0.92) 40%,
    rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 100%
  );
}

/* ── Content ── */
.container {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.hero-inner {
  padding: 100px 0 64px;
  max-width: 640px;
}

.hero-title {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: clamp(3.25rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.15;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.hero-sub {
  font-size: 1.0625rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
}

.hero-desc {
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.9;
  margin-bottom: 44px;
  max-width: 520px;
}

.hero-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 14px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

/* ── Stats ── */
.hero-stats {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 28px 40px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  width: fit-content;
  gap: 0;
}

.stat-item {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 0 36px;
}

.stat-item:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
.stat-item:last-child  { padding-right: 0; }

.stat-num {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 2.25rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--text);
}

.stat-num small {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 500;
}

.stat-text {
  font-size: 0.725rem;
  color: var(--text-light);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}

.stat-sep {
  width: 1px;
  height: 36px;
  background: var(--border);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero-kv-overlay {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
  }
  .hero-inner { padding: 64px 0 48px; }
  .hero-stats {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .stat-sep { display: none; }
  .stat-item {
    padding: 0;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 80px;
  }
}
</style>
